name: Fox and Crocodile
description: This artwork is a part of The Gondwana Art Project, a tribal art initiative from central India • Medium: Acrylic and cow dung on cloth • Artist: Anita Balu Mhase • Style: Warli • The original physical artwork (Size: 48 in x 36 in) is also available for purchase, please contact us at ccdfindia@gmail.com
